query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) as properties_with_images, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM properties) as total_properties, ROUND(100.0 * COUNT(DISTINCT property_id) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM properties), 2) as percentage_with_images FROM property_images;
